{"tid":533947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭國會通過確立東部為俄羅斯佔領區 必要時將動武","createTime":"2018-01-19T10:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:34:29.000Z","uid":60545,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4072ecacd6a4125d7a28b539333e8c6ec996db","tid":533947,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】烏克蘭國會通過法案，確立被俄羅斯控制的東部地區為「被佔領」區，必要時會以武力奪回。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭國會投票表決，通過確立東部頓涅茨克和盧甘斯克兩個州是被侵略國俄羅斯暫時佔領地區的法案，並不惜以武力奪回東部地區。<br />\n<br />\n總統波羅申科表示歡迎，認為法案有助國家在政治及外交層面上收復東部失地。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外交部就批評，法案埋葬了由多國斡旋使成的明斯克停火協議，同時引起東部民眾反感，令烏克蘭進一步分裂。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯2014年強行吞併克里米亞，並支持東部親俄分子爭取獨立，與烏克蘭軍方爆發武裝衝突，其後國際社會介入，一年後促成簽訂明斯克停火協議，但雙方多次違反停火協定，協議形同虛設。<br />\n<br />\n衝突近日更有升級迹象，估計過去三年最少已有超過一萬人在衝突中死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=250963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D250963&d=O%2FDIUHGNus3%2BZXxg%2BPUTdf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=bf9b358e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D250963&h=5b3e7efb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=250963</a>"},{"pid":"509eb4794d8464ab7a4a633454ad2f245830e847","tid":533947,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"無北約幫手點會打"},{"pid":"ace1f2ae4cae613c5e80b06f5f6bcc2da31a5392","tid":533947,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66513b853f659604b2fe67e2dc98ddf9cb5bd37e","tid":533947,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"支持自決獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}